WEBVTT

00:00:22.140 --> 00:00:27.260
♪Embark on a farewell
without saying goodbye♪

00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:32.020
♪Build a bridge between life and death♪

00:00:32.380 --> 00:00:36.300
♪Hear a voiceless declaration♪

00:00:36.660 --> 00:00:41.500
♪Break disguises, cross illusions♪

00:00:41.860 --> 00:00:44.420
♪A fleeting life and delusions♪

00:00:44.420 --> 00:00:47.260
♪The surface always conceals♪

00:00:47.260 --> 00:00:52.300
♪Separate cause and effect♪

00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:55.180
♪A twisted path, rising and falling♪

00:00:55.180 --> 00:00:57.820
♪Seek the path amid the hazy unknown♪

00:00:57.820 --> 00:01:02.660
♪Writing oblivion with a sharp blade♪

00:01:02.660 --> 00:01:07.540
♪No matter how far, I gaze at the light♪

00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:13.100
♪Fearing no wild lands, I press on♪

00:01:13.540 --> 00:01:18.580
♪To see the tides of the world
once more♪

00:01:18.940 --> 00:01:23.860
♪The deeper truth is buried, it grows♪

00:01:24.220 --> 00:01:26.220
♪Until it is set free♪

00:01:35.380 --> 00:01:40.820
=The Imperial Coroner S2=
(Adapted from Idle Girl's The Constable's Wife)

00:01:40.820 --> 00:01:43.900
(This story is entirely fictional.)

00:01:44.599 --> 00:01:45.519
(My name is Chu Chu.)

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:47.290
(I admired Handsome Judge
since I was young.)

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:49.359
(I vowed to become
an excellent coroner,)

00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:51.319
(so I went alone to Chang'an)

00:01:51.320 --> 00:01:53.330
(to take the Three Judicial Offices'
coroner exam.)

00:01:53.879 --> 00:01:56.159
(But I mistook His Highness for a test)

00:01:56.400 --> 00:01:58.480
(and nearly stripped him in public.)

00:01:59.560 --> 00:02:00.200
(Fortunately,)

00:02:00.239 --> 00:02:02.519
(the prince with godlike judgment)

00:02:02.760 --> 00:02:04.959
(gave me a chance to prove myself.)

00:02:05.400 --> 00:02:06.359
(I gave it my all)

00:02:06.599 --> 00:02:08.319
(and used my unique coroner skills)

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:10.120
(to stay in the Three Judicial Offices.)

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:12.560
(From then on, every day began)

00:02:12.719 --> 00:02:14.520
(with the joy of examining bodies.)

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:15.759
(There,)

00:02:16.159 --> 00:02:17.520
(I met new close friends.)

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:19.039
(Vice Minister Jing,)

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:20.319
(clever, sharp,)

00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:22.759
(and skilled at reading people and lies.)

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:24.479
(Miss Leng,)

00:02:24.840 --> 00:02:26.080
(highly skilled in martial arts)

00:02:26.199 --> 00:02:27.360
(and deeply righteous.)

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:29.759
(She was injured protecting me,)

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:31.639
(yet she comforted me instead.)

00:02:32.479 --> 00:02:34.159
(I used my coroner skills)

00:02:34.439 --> 00:02:36.520
(to recreate scenes with His Highness.)

00:02:36.919 --> 00:02:39.319
(Together, we solved a major case
threatening the throne.)

00:02:40.039 --> 00:02:42.039
(I was thus commended by His Majesty)

00:02:42.280 --> 00:02:44.599
(and granted the title
Imperial Coroner.)

00:02:54.639 --> 00:02:56.680
(His Highness and I
fell in love amid danger.)

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:58.599
(We're husband and wife)

00:02:59.080 --> 00:03:00.840
(and also partners in battle.)

00:03:01.919 --> 00:03:03.199
(Life after marriage)

00:03:03.479 --> 00:03:05.240
(is sweet and fulfilling.)

00:03:06.280 --> 00:03:07.000
(In a blink,)

00:03:07.599 --> 00:03:08.879
(three years passed.)

00:03:12.940 --> 00:03:16.100
=Episode 1=

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:23.479
(Late mid-Tang dynasty,)

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:26.479
(Emperor Xuanzong governed tirelessly.)

00:03:27.039 --> 00:03:28.639
(He established Three Judicial Offices)

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:30.960
(and appointed
Commandery Prince An Xiao Jinyu)

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:33.360
(to oversee all criminal justice,)

00:03:33.719 --> 00:03:35.080
(punish evil,)

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:36.599
(redress injustices,)

00:03:36.840 --> 00:03:38.280
(and uphold order.)

00:03:38.919 --> 00:03:42.120
(Yet villains still stirred.)

00:03:42.280 --> 00:03:44.639
(And neighboring nations
watched with predatory eyes.)

00:03:45.479 --> 00:03:47.879
(On the Emperor's birthday,)

00:03:48.240 --> 00:03:49.039
(all realms)

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:51.719
(sent envoys to the court.)

00:03:53.660 --> 00:03:54.620
It's already this month.

00:03:54.639 --> 00:03:55.580
Why is it still so cold?

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:56.719
Here.

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:58.439
Have some liquor.

00:03:58.520 --> 00:03:59.360
It'll warm you up.

00:04:05.319 --> 00:04:06.599
It's quiet tonight.

00:04:08.199 --> 00:04:09.719
Tomorrow is the Emperor's birthday.

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:10.719
The curfew is lifted.

00:04:10.840 --> 00:04:12.039
That's when we'll be busy.

00:04:12.599 --> 00:04:14.360
With pay that little,

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.680
let's just patrol casually.

00:04:16.319 --> 00:04:18.360
All is perfectly peaceful
under the Emperor's nose.

00:04:19.720 --> 00:04:20.480
What was that?

00:04:38.319 --> 00:04:39.560
Stay alert.

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:41.580
Envoys arrive
for the birthday banquet tomorrow.

00:04:41.720 --> 00:04:43.000
No mistakes are allowed.

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:43.879
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:04:44.560 --> 00:04:45.480
If any of you

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:47.600
mess this up at this moment,

00:04:47.879 --> 00:04:49.639
don't blame me for showing no mercy.

00:04:58.639 --> 00:04:59.279
He's here.

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:00.439
He's here again.

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:02.240
Why are you so clumsy?

00:05:02.319 --> 00:05:02.959
What's here?

00:05:03.839 --> 00:05:04.279
A ghost.

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:05.480
It's haunted.

00:05:05.879 --> 00:05:06.519
A ghost?

00:05:07.439 --> 00:05:09.279
There are endless ghost tales
in the palace.

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:10.240
Who has seen a real one?

00:05:10.330 --> 00:05:11.000
Get back to work.

00:05:47.900 --> 00:05:50.260
(Three Judicial Offices)

00:06:04.180 --> 00:06:08.660
(Chu Chu, Imperial Coroner,
Commandery Princess Consort An)

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:10.000
Your Highness, look.

00:06:10.140 --> 00:06:11.720
(Xiao Jinyu, Commandery Prince An)

00:06:11.720 --> 00:06:12.319
What is it?

00:06:13.720 --> 00:06:15.319
The fontanelle sits too low.

00:06:15.839 --> 00:06:16.920
The frontal bone protrudes.

00:06:17.500 --> 00:06:18.790
The temporal bones flare outward.

00:06:19.600 --> 00:06:22.240
Between the parietal
and occipital bones lacks fullness.

00:06:23.319 --> 00:06:24.519
Is something wrong?

00:06:27.920 --> 00:06:31.279
If the hair is styled like this,
my skull looks poorly matched to yours.

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:32.560
Skull?

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:34.759
Matched to me?

00:06:35.240 --> 00:06:36.800
Eyes can deceive.

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:38.639
Once the hair is done,

00:06:38.759 --> 00:06:40.399
it can make a person's whole skull

00:06:40.480 --> 00:06:42.600
look better than it truly is.

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:46.000
Your skull is naturally excellent.

00:06:46.920 --> 00:06:48.759
I must style my hair properly

00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:51.120
to look better matched to you.

00:06:51.759 --> 00:06:52.759
Let me have a look.

00:06:57.040 --> 00:06:58.839
How could
Commandery Princess Consort An lie?

00:06:59.560 --> 00:07:01.000
We're clearly a perfect match.

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:08.199
The birthday banquet is just a meal.

00:07:08.700 --> 00:07:09.720
No need to be so nervous.

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:11.720
Rest assured.

00:07:12.079 --> 00:07:13.519
I've learned the palace rules.

00:07:13.959 --> 00:07:15.000
I won't embarrass us

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:17.079
nor Three Judicial Offices.

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:19.970
You're busy daily
at the Three Judicial Offices.

00:07:20.580 --> 00:07:22.199
Where did you find time to hire a tutor?

00:07:22.839 --> 00:07:23.959
Not a tutor.

00:07:24.639 --> 00:07:25.399
It was Leng Yue.

00:07:25.759 --> 00:07:26.600
Leng Yue?

00:07:30.959 --> 00:07:33.639
These rules are not absolutely necessary.

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:34.900
After being married so long,

00:07:35.199 --> 00:07:37.279
this is my first formal palace banquet.

00:07:37.600 --> 00:07:39.000
I'm Commandery Princess Consort An.

00:07:39.199 --> 00:07:40.439
I can't embarrass ourselves.

00:07:40.800 --> 00:07:42.920
I'm the one troubling you
to spare time to go with me.

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:44.839
You willing to go

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:46.879
already makes me very grateful.

00:07:59.199 --> 00:07:59.800
Chu Chu.

00:08:00.839 --> 00:08:01.439
Chu Chu.

00:08:02.780 --> 00:08:03.920
(Leng Yue, Daughter
of Qianzhongdao's Leng family)

00:08:03.920 --> 00:08:04.519
Chu Chu.

00:08:05.399 --> 00:08:07.639
I brought you
clothes and grooming items.

00:08:08.920 --> 00:08:10.720
When will you learn
to knock before entering?

00:08:11.399 --> 00:08:12.759
And you teach others etiquette?

00:08:14.520 --> 00:08:15.580
Sorry to disturb you both.

00:08:15.959 --> 00:08:16.560
Leng Yue.

00:08:16.759 --> 00:08:18.439
Why did you deliver these yourself?

00:08:18.660 --> 00:08:19.399
Where is Wu Jiang?

00:08:20.839 --> 00:08:23.199
It seems our carriage
is stuck at the West Market.

00:08:23.400 --> 00:08:24.480
She happened to run into it.

00:08:24.639 --> 00:08:25.439
How do you know?

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:27.880
The petal shaped paper scraps
in your hair bun

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:29.439
were thrown during the shop opening.

00:08:30.040 --> 00:08:30.480
Move aside.

00:08:30.839 --> 00:08:31.319
Move aside.

00:08:36.279 --> 00:08:37.879
The gold dust on your clothes and bag

00:08:38.300 --> 00:08:39.730
comes from the scarves hung outside

00:08:39.919 --> 00:08:41.639
West Market tailor shops year round.

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:48.159
The moss on your hem and shoes

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:50.279
shows you took a shortcut.

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:53.639
A shortcut that draws all eyes.

00:08:54.759 --> 00:08:56.159
- Good.
- Good.

00:08:56.800 --> 00:08:58.350
People of Commandery Prince An's Mansion

00:08:58.360 --> 00:09:00.250
really lack experience
with joining in the fun.

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:01.720
Today is the Emperor's birthday.

00:09:01.799 --> 00:09:02.799
The city is packed.

00:09:03.050 --> 00:09:05.190
Yet Wu Jiang still drove a carriage
to deliver things.

00:09:08.919 --> 00:09:09.480
Are you

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:11.320
doing your hair here?

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:14.279
I have too much work to return home.

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:14.919
It happens

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:17.240
the tools used for preparing bodies
are all here,

00:09:17.500 --> 00:09:18.840
so I asked His Highness for help.

00:09:20.759 --> 00:09:21.559
Since you're here,

00:09:21.879 --> 00:09:22.840
I'll go prepare as well.

00:09:23.700 --> 00:09:24.279
See you soon.

00:09:55.180 --> 00:09:57.160
(Jing Yi, Vice Minister
of the Court of Judicial Review)

00:09:59.860 --> 00:10:01.480
(Xiao Jinli, Marquis Duyu)

00:10:01.480 --> 00:10:03.600
Commandery Prince An's reach is too far.

00:10:04.200 --> 00:10:05.279
His Three Judicial Offices

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:08.279
now manage all major and minor cases
in Chang'an.

00:10:08.879 --> 00:10:10.000
(Jiang Daohai, Prefect of the Capital)
Capital security.

00:10:10.320 --> 00:10:11.720
(Liu Shijiang, Prefect of Jiaozhou)
Reassignment of offending officials.

00:10:11.799 --> 00:10:12.399
Even

00:10:12.559 --> 00:10:13.639
envoys from afar

00:10:13.799 --> 00:10:15.360
(Huang Lv, Vice Minister of Rites)
must follow his rules.

00:10:15.960 --> 00:10:17.039
He wouldn't even spare

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:19.879
a bit of allowance
for us censors from various prefectures.

00:10:20.559 --> 00:10:21.440
Allowance?

00:10:21.720 --> 00:10:22.440
Sirs.

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.480
We officials in the capital

00:10:24.600 --> 00:10:26.759
are lucky just to have our pay.

00:10:28.840 --> 00:10:29.840
Prefect of the Capital.

00:10:30.159 --> 00:10:30.960
Speak freely.

00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:32.120
Speak freely.

00:10:34.480 --> 00:10:36.480
Everyone has their own agenda,

00:10:36.919 --> 00:10:39.519
except they unite against Jinyu.

00:10:39.560 --> 00:10:41.240
(Zhao Zhaoning, Consort Hui)

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:42.240
If we say

00:10:42.799 --> 00:10:45.039
(Zhao Wanrong, Wife of Prefect of the Capital)
the model among the capital's women,

00:10:46.639 --> 00:10:47.989
(Jiang Yufen)
Commandery Princess Consort An

00:10:47.989 --> 00:10:49.440
(Wife of Vice Minister Zhao of Ministry of Rites)
would definitely have a place.

00:10:49.519 --> 00:10:52.279
I heard from the previous
Prefect of Qianzhou's wife

00:10:52.759 --> 00:10:53.840
(Shi Qing, Consort Hui's Chief Maid)
that Commandery Prince An

00:10:53.960 --> 00:10:56.039
even personally
made a set o autopsy tools

00:10:56.080 --> 00:10:57.500
for Commandery Princess Consort An.

00:10:57.919 --> 00:10:59.559
What a sinister token of love.

00:10:59.840 --> 00:11:02.240
Commandery Princess Consort An
is extraordinary.

00:11:02.480 --> 00:11:04.720
She spends her days
in coroner's clothes,

00:11:04.919 --> 00:11:06.399
digging among corpses.

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:08.720
That coroner outfit
is my official uniform.

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:10.399
Look, His Highness and Jing Yi

00:11:10.440 --> 00:11:12.480
can wear uniforms at palace banquets.

00:11:12.759 --> 00:11:13.519
I can't.

00:11:13.759 --> 00:11:14.440
Clothes

00:11:14.799 --> 00:11:17.120
are just for decorating fools.

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:19.480
You're Tang Dynasty's
first imperial coroner.

00:11:20.620 --> 00:11:22.759
You're granted personally
by His Majesty. That's rare.

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:24.320
I believe

00:11:24.759 --> 00:11:25.720
that one day

00:11:25.960 --> 00:11:28.000
you'll wear this coroner outfit
in the palace.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:29.159
You're right.

00:11:30.080 --> 00:11:32.039
At today's banquet, I'll show them

00:11:32.559 --> 00:11:35.080
a coroner princess consort
is no worse than any lady.

00:11:38.919 --> 00:11:40.919
Commandery Prince An has arrived.

00:11:51.480 --> 00:11:52.480
- Commandery Prince An.
- Commandery Prince An.

00:11:52.559 --> 00:11:53.799
- Commandery Prince An.
- Commandery Prince An.

00:11:54.039 --> 00:11:54.880
Commandery Prince An.

00:11:59.279 --> 00:12:00.399
- Commandery Prince An.
- Commandery Prince An.

00:12:00.480 --> 00:12:02.440
Our Xinluo tea is famous far and wide.

00:12:02.639 --> 00:12:03.879
When you're free,

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:04.840
please try some.

00:12:04.850 --> 00:12:05.680
Commandery Prince An,

00:12:05.690 --> 00:12:07.880
our envoy has been taken
by the Three Judicial Offices

00:12:07.890 --> 00:12:09.000
for over a month.

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:10.279
Why not let him

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:11.639
invite you elsewhere for tea?

00:12:11.750 --> 00:12:12.590
Commandery Prince An.

00:12:12.840 --> 00:12:14.799
My suburban house
has clear mountains and waters

00:12:14.800 --> 00:12:15.700
and beautiful scenery.

00:12:16.039 --> 00:12:16.720
Take a look.

00:12:16.879 --> 00:12:18.279
Flowers bloom in splendor.

00:12:18.840 --> 00:12:20.159
Cooking fires flare.

00:12:31.519 --> 00:12:33.559
Ladies and ministers sit separately.

00:12:33.960 --> 00:12:35.720
Noble ladies are in the inner section.

00:12:36.300 --> 00:12:37.380
(Commandery Princess Consort An
has arrived.)

00:12:37.399 --> 00:12:38.000
Currently,

00:12:38.559 --> 00:12:40.720
Consort Hui manages the six palaces.

00:12:41.200 --> 00:12:42.879
The ladies all honor her.

00:12:43.519 --> 00:12:43.960
Exactly.

00:12:45.200 --> 00:12:45.660
By the way,

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:49.399
if she asks about your work
at the Three Judicial Offices...

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:50.919
Don't reveal everything truthfully.

00:12:51.000 --> 00:12:52.399
We show our faces daily,

00:12:52.400 --> 00:12:54.799
but the palace forbids private contact
between men and women.

00:12:55.399 --> 00:12:58.399
Maids and guards are punished
for minor interactions.

00:12:59.919 --> 00:13:01.840
Tang law has no such rule.

00:13:02.279 --> 00:13:03.399
Law is law.

00:13:03.600 --> 00:13:04.799
Palace rules are palace rules.

00:13:04.960 --> 00:13:06.360
Let's not argue with them.

00:13:08.279 --> 00:13:08.919
Congratulations.

00:13:09.360 --> 00:13:10.720
Like Commandery Prince An,

00:13:11.200 --> 00:13:12.879
you'll become
a thorn in everyone's eyes.

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:14.799
Your tea leaves

00:13:15.000 --> 00:13:16.279
far exceed reported amounts.

00:13:16.280 --> 00:13:17.490
You're suspected of private sale.

00:13:17.519 --> 00:13:18.440
Your envoy

00:13:18.559 --> 00:13:20.799
visited 18 of our officials in a month,

00:13:21.080 --> 00:13:22.519
gifting over 10,000 taels of silver.

00:13:23.039 --> 00:13:23.600
You

00:13:23.759 --> 00:13:25.919
occupy suburban fields
to build a private mansions.

00:13:25.920 --> 00:13:27.900
Three Judicial Offices seized them
in accordance with the law.

00:13:27.919 --> 00:13:28.879
Tea is unnecessary.

00:13:29.080 --> 00:13:30.639
Handle official business first.

00:13:31.480 --> 00:13:33.159
We're all foreign envoys.

00:13:34.639 --> 00:13:36.200
Seeking friendship with you

00:13:36.279 --> 00:13:37.759
is a matter of diplomacy.

00:13:38.279 --> 00:13:40.320
But your actions

00:13:40.480 --> 00:13:42.519
show disregard for us.

00:13:46.559 --> 00:13:47.639
Tang law

00:13:48.159 --> 00:13:49.039
applies to all.

00:13:50.480 --> 00:13:54.120
Coincidentally, Three Judicial Offices,
have official matters needing your help.

00:13:54.840 --> 00:13:55.799
I fear

00:13:56.279 --> 00:13:58.600
(Gao Luoqian, Vice Envoy of Nanzhao)
I can't help you.

00:13:58.610 --> 00:14:01.200
According to Three Judicial Offices'
investigation, recent years,

00:14:01.360 --> 00:14:03.600
many border villagers
were lured with high wages

00:14:03.780 --> 00:14:05.720
and tricked
into illegally crossing to Nanzhao.

00:14:05.960 --> 00:14:09.480
Three Judicial Offices have investigated
but many remain missing.

00:14:10.279 --> 00:14:12.240
We hope Nanzhao will assist
as much as possible

00:14:12.279 --> 00:14:15.159
to apprehend the wanted criminals
and return Tang's missing citizens,

00:14:15.440 --> 00:14:16.639
so they can come home soon.

00:14:16.650 --> 00:14:18.620
We want to see them,
whether they're alive or dead.

00:14:18.639 --> 00:14:19.879
Then the case may be closed.

00:14:20.180 --> 00:14:22.039
And justice
will be restored to the victims.

00:14:25.679 --> 00:14:27.200
Greetings, Your Highness.

00:14:28.960 --> 00:14:30.320
Please rise.

