I feel like

00:17:35.319 --> 00:17:36.160
she's

00:17:36.559 --> 00:17:37.799
treating the roasted meat

00:17:38.240 --> 00:17:39.519
as a corpse.

00:18:01.880 --> 00:18:02.920
Protect the Emperor!

00:18:03.759 --> 00:18:05.200
Protect the Emperor!

