The skull is moving.

00:18:44.559 --> 00:18:44.960
Ghost!

00:18:45.480 --> 00:18:46.319
- Ghost!
- Ghost!

00:18:46.320 --> 00:18:47.700
- There's a ghost!
- There's a ghost!

00:18:52.559 --> 00:18:53.359
What happened?

00:18:55.279 --> 00:18:56.039
Don't panic.

00:18:56.400 --> 00:18:58.039
