00:20:06.039 --> 00:20:07.200
Mandible angle is wide.

00:20:07.279 --> 00:20:08.319
Zygomatic arch is strong.

00:20:08.519 --> 00:20:09.799
It should be an adult male.

00:20:10.440 --> 00:20:11.920
(Teeth Wear)
Judging from the teeth,

00:20:12.039 --> 00:20:13.090
he was about 30 years old.

00:20:13.279 --> 00:20:14.480
Orbital edges are rounded,

00:20:14.799 --> 00:20:15.759
and nose is sunken.

00:20:16.050 --> 00:20:17.920
These are features
of a Central Plains person.

00:20:20.799 --> 00:20:23.640
During decomposition,
the body was covered in algae.

00:20:23.660 --> 00:20:25.880
It must have been soaking there
for at least half a year.

00:20:25.880 --> 00:20:27.060
- Half a year?
- Half a year?

00:20:31.000 --> 00:20:32.920
Your Highness, forgive me.
I arrived late.

00:20:37.010 --> 00:20:39.800
We'll take the remains away immediately
and investigate thoroughly.

00:20:44.079 --> 00:20:45.000
Just put it in here.

00:20:49.800 --> 00:20:51.100
Commandery Princess Consort An.

00:20:51.250 --> 00:20:53.480
I know you're the coroner
of the Three Judicial Offices,

00:20:53.500 --> 00:20:55.200
but this matter
happened inside the palace

00:20:55.210 --> 00:20:56.990
and should be handled
by the palace official.

00:20:58.039 --> 00:20:59.839
Do you know who the deceased is?

00:21:03.039 --> 00:21:04.119
How would I know?

00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:05.880
The palace guards are strict,

00:21:05.900 --> 00:21:07.359
and all entries are logged in detail.

00:21:07.920 --> 00:21:10.519
The deceased is very likely someone
from the palace.

00:21:10.520 --> 00:21:12.270
You oversee the six palaces, Your Highness.

00:21:12.319 --> 00:21:14.119
