had been missing for this long,

00:21:14.120 --> 00:21:15.920
it should have been
reported to you already.

00:21:16.119 --> 00:21:16.640
Impudent.

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:18.370
Are you interrogating Her Highness?

00:21:19.400 --> 00:21:20.119
Moreover,

00:21:20.519 --> 00:21:21.839
if he died unnaturally,

00:21:22.119 --> 00:21:24.559
the culprit could very well
be someone in the palace.

00:21:24.799 --> 00:21:26.920
Commandery Princess Consort An,
don't scare us.

00:21:27.079 --> 00:21:29.559
Today, many foreign envoys
are here for the banquet.

00:21:29.640 --> 00:21:31.480
You insist on making this unlucky matter

00:21:31.519 --> 00:21:32.680
widely known.

00:21:32.920 --> 00:21:34.000
What are your intentions?

00:21:34.599 --> 00:21:35.160
Jinbao.

00:21:35.839 --> 00:21:38.480
Arrange for the ministers
to go to Ziyun House for the banquet.

00:21:38.960 --> 00:21:39.519
Yes.

00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:45.820
Why are you standing there?

00:21:45.839 --> 00:21:46.400
Go

00:21:46.480 --> 00:21:47.400
and remove the filth.

00:21:47.720 --> 00:21:49.990
If you disturb His Majesty,
you will pay with your heads.

00:21:51.520 --> 00:21:52.079
How dare you?

00:21:52.080 --> 00:21:53.990
Dare you offend
Commandery Princess Consort An?

00:21:56.119 --> 00:21:58.240
Leave her to me then.

00:22:00.680 --> 00:22:01.519
Miss Shi Qing.

00:22:14.200 --> 00:22:14.759
Enough.

00:22:22.500 --> 00:22:23.359
Commandery Prince An.

00:22:23.759 --> 00:22:24.519
Vice Minister Jing.

00:22:25.119 --> 00:22:26.200
Come with me to take a look.

00:22:26.319 --> 00:22:26.880
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:22:32.680 --> 00:22:34.480
How dare you
be so reckless in the palace,

00:22:34.490 --> 00:22:36.200
disobeying superiors
and spreading rumors?

00:22:36.210 --> 00:22:38.450
If not punished severely,
how can palace rules be upheld?

00:22:38.700 --> 00:22:39.279
Your Highness.

00:22:39.500 --> 00:22:42.319
Commandery Princess Consort An acted
for your safety and His Majesty's.

00:22:42.359 --> 00:22:44.640
His Majesty has arrived.

00:22:45.210 --> 00:22:48.290
- We respectfully welcome Your Majesty.
- We respectfully welcome Your Majesty.

00:22:49.190 --> 00:22:50.039
No need for ceremony.

00:22:50.559 --> 00:22:51.520
Thank you, Your Majesty.

00:22:51.720 --> 00:22:52.480
What happened?

00:22:55.800 --> 00:22:56.920
Reporting to Your Majesty.

00:22:57.119 --> 00:22:58.039
A palace staff

00:22:58.240 --> 00:23:00.200
was found drowned in the pond.

00:23:00.519 --> 00:23:01.720
I'm handling it.

