00:25:19.759 --> 00:25:21.599
Those close to him would know this well.

00:25:22.520 --> 00:25:24.240
Check with the guards
and eunuchs tomorrow.

00:25:24.360 --> 00:25:24.960
Leave it to me.

00:25:25.820 --> 00:25:26.880
As for the palace maids...

00:25:26.890 --> 00:25:28.780
It's easier for me and Leng Yue
to speak with them.

00:25:28.799 --> 00:25:29.880
We'll go together tomorrow.

00:25:30.440 --> 00:25:30.880
Alright.

00:25:31.519 --> 00:25:32.319
Sorry to trouble you

00:25:32.480 --> 00:25:33.759
to haul up the body tonight.

00:25:34.079 --> 00:25:35.079
Why so polite?

00:25:35.519 --> 00:25:37.519
Staying up to handle work
is our specialty.

00:25:39.240 --> 00:25:40.079
Hurry back.

00:25:40.319 --> 00:25:41.000
Hurry.

00:25:48.400 --> 00:25:49.680
What's the matter with you today?

00:25:50.440 --> 00:25:51.640
I behaved improperly.

00:25:52.150 --> 00:25:53.480
I beg Your Majesty for punishment.

00:25:53.799 --> 00:25:55.799
You've managed the harem for years.

00:25:56.359 --> 00:25:59.440
You're always composed and generous,
handling matters meticulously.

