Even the King of Hell has to let him
check the Book of Life and Death.

00:27:47.759 --> 00:27:49.440
If he discovers anything...

00:27:50.400 --> 00:27:51.359
It's my negligence.

00:27:51.360 --> 00:27:53.580
I truly didn't expect
Three Judicial Offices to overstep

00:27:53.599 --> 00:27:54.680
into the inner palace.

00:27:56.680 --> 00:27:57.480
If it comes to

00:27:58.480 --> 00:28:00.319
the day even I can't protect this...

00:28:00.480 --> 00:28:01.759
She'll know what to do.

00:28:05.980 --> 00:28:07.300
(Discern the bigger picture
from small hints)

00:28:15.039 --> 00:28:16.000
You've worked hard.

00:28:16.880 --> 00:28:17.559
It's so late,

00:28:17.660 --> 00:28:19.100
and you're still studying this skull.

00:28:19.119 --> 00:28:20.119
It's so heavy.

00:28:20.160 --> 00:28:21.960
My neck is getting stiff.

00:28:22.310 --> 00:28:23.390
I'll take it apart for you.

00:28:23.960 --> 00:28:24.359
Here.

