00:28:30.519 --> 00:28:32.640
It's my fault
for neglecting social ties,

00:28:33.359 --> 00:28:34.400
causing you to be wronged.

00:28:35.400 --> 00:28:37.200
I'll explain things to Consort Hui.

00:28:38.000 --> 00:28:38.559
Don't worry.

00:28:40.000 --> 00:28:41.200
I was careless.

00:28:41.599 --> 00:28:44.039
I've always
tried to be mindful of my status,

00:28:44.599 --> 00:28:45.480
but

00:28:45.880 --> 00:28:48.079
when I see this corpse and case,

00:28:48.519 --> 00:28:49.359
I can't help myself.

00:28:50.240 --> 00:28:51.720
And I caused such a mess.

00:28:51.839 --> 00:28:52.640
I'm sorry.

00:28:55.060 --> 00:28:56.039
Does your shoulder hurt?

00:28:56.520 --> 00:28:57.550
I'll massage them for you.

00:29:01.559 --> 00:29:02.119
Your Highness.

00:29:02.880 --> 00:29:05.160
Guess what I was thinking

00:29:05.500 --> 00:29:06.500
while holding this skull?

00:29:06.759 --> 00:29:07.440
What?

00:29:07.960 --> 00:29:08.559
As expected,

00:29:08.759 --> 00:29:10.000
most people's skulls

00:29:10.039 --> 00:29:11.119
aren't as pretty as yours.

00:29:12.660 --> 00:29:14.960
If it wasn't pretty,
you wouldn't have held it so tightly.

00:29:15.839 --> 00:29:17.279
My beautiful skull

00:29:17.319 --> 00:29:18.800
has never been held like this before.

00:29:19.119 --> 00:29:21.559
If someone tried to dispose
of your skull recklessly,

00:29:21.599 --> 00:29:23.000
I wouldn't let go either.

00:29:24.640 --> 00:29:26.480
Then my skull thanks you in advance.

00:29:26.480 --> 00:29:28.300
(Discern the bigger picture
from small hints)

00:29:37.880 --> 00:29:38.440
Ouch.

00:29:47.680 --> 00:29:48.559
Bold thief.

00:29:48.560 --> 00:29:49.990
You've broken
into the Three Judicial Offices.

00:29:50.240 --> 00:29:51.039
I'm not a thief.

00:29:51.040 --> 00:29:52.290
I came here openly and honestly.

00:29:52.559 --> 00:29:53.160
Girl.

00:29:53.480 --> 00:29:54.119
Help.

00:29:54.440 --> 00:29:55.079
Girl?

00:29:57.680 --> 00:29:58.240
Chu He?

00:29:58.480 --> 00:29:58.920
Who?

00:29:59.319 --> 00:29:59.960
Go.

00:30:01.119 --> 00:30:01.640
He.

00:30:02.200 --> 00:30:03.079
Are you alright?

00:30:03.480 --> 00:30:04.319
Why are you here?

00:30:04.640 --> 00:30:06.890
(Chu He, Chu Chu's Brother)
Of course I came to see you.

00:30:06.900 --> 00:30:08.340
I only found out you hadn't been back

00:30:08.359 --> 00:30:09.990
to the mansion in a long time
after going there.

00:30:10.119 --> 00:30:11.359
(Wu Jiang)
That's why I came here.

00:30:11.759 --> 00:30:12.519
(Commandery Prince An's Guard)
Mr. Chu.

00:30:12.720 --> 00:30:13.720
Be the bigger person.

00:30:14.039 --> 00:30:15.079
I didn't hold back

00:30:15.359 --> 00:30:16.240
just now.

00:30:16.799 --> 00:30:18.200
You know I'm Mr. Chu?

00:30:19.160 --> 00:30:19.920
I knew it.

00:30:20.039 --> 00:30:21.690
Three Judicial Offices
is heavily guarded.

00:30:22.079 --> 00:30:24.000
No ordinary petty thief could get in.

00:30:25.160 --> 00:30:27.759
Chu Chu sent a letter praising
Commandery Prince An's Mansion.

00:30:28.079 --> 00:30:29.160
I had to see it myself

00:30:29.319 --> 00:30:30.519
whether she was wronged.

00:30:31.200 --> 00:30:31.559
He.

00:30:31.839 --> 00:30:32.759
Good thing I came.

00:30:32.760 --> 00:30:34.870
Why is being a princess consort
even harder than before?

00:30:34.880 --> 00:30:36.230
You're still up at this late hour.

00:30:36.240 --> 00:30:37.950
Three Judicial Offices
have been busy recently.

00:30:37.960 --> 00:30:38.920
I wasn't considerate.

00:30:39.240 --> 00:30:41.119
And there's a case
at today's birthday banquet.

00:30:41.120 --> 00:30:42.700
That's why we've been working until now.

00:30:43.800 --> 00:30:45.780
I'll make sure she gets more rest
in the future.

00:30:46.039 --> 00:30:47.480
Future?

00:30:47.759 --> 00:30:48.720
Go rest now.

00:30:50.799 --> 00:30:51.359
Wu Jiang.

00:30:52.039 --> 00:30:53.240
Take my brother back first.

00:30:53.720 --> 00:30:54.759
I'll tidy up for a bit.

00:30:54.880 --> 00:30:56.319
I'll be back right after.

00:30:56.519 --> 00:30:57.119
Girl.

00:30:57.160 --> 00:30:57.880
I'll be back soon.

00:30:58.000 --> 00:30:58.440
Mr. Chu.

00:30:58.599 --> 00:30:59.039
This way.

00:30:59.210 --> 00:31:00.680
I even prepared the bathwater for you.

00:31:12.839 --> 00:31:14.319
My brother has always been like this,

00:31:14.480 --> 00:31:16.640
worrying about whether I'm doing well.

00:31:16.640 --> 00:31:17.480
(Lian Qiao, Chu Chu's Personal Maid)

00:31:17.480 --> 00:31:19.240
I'm all grown up now,

00:31:19.440 --> 00:31:21.279
but he still treats me like I'm a child.

00:31:21.880 --> 00:31:23.319
He's not worried about you,

00:31:23.519 --> 00:31:24.559
he's worried about me.

00:31:25.240 --> 00:31:26.160
Worried about you?

00:31:26.480 --> 00:31:27.400
Worried about what?

00:31:28.400 --> 00:31:29.680
He's worried that I'd bully you.

00:31:32.279 --> 00:31:32.839
Your Highness.

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:33.559
Your Highness.

00:31:33.960 --> 00:31:35.240
Mr. Chu came.

00:31:38.200 --> 00:31:38.799
Wow.

00:31:40.160 --> 00:31:40.480
This...

00:31:40.759 --> 00:31:42.000
This is my home.

00:31:42.400 --> 00:31:43.160
From Qianzhou?

00:31:43.319 --> 00:31:43.759
Yes.

00:31:43.839 --> 00:31:44.640
Remember?

00:31:44.839 --> 00:31:46.599
These are all from my home in Qianzhou.

00:31:51.039 --> 00:31:51.920
Wow.

00:31:52.559 --> 00:31:54.200
I made this little dog myself.

00:31:54.210 --> 00:31:55.130
Does it look like real?

00:31:57.240 --> 00:31:57.680
It does.

00:32:00.000 --> 00:32:01.640
When I first wanted to be a coroner,

00:32:01.680 --> 00:32:02.759
Yamen wouldn't accept me.

00:32:02.810 --> 00:32:04.519
They said no woman
had ever been a coroner.

00:32:05.000 --> 00:32:06.680
Even my brother
took in other apprentices,

00:32:06.720 --> 00:32:07.640
but wouldn't take me.

00:32:08.079 --> 00:32:08.920
Many of these manuals

00:32:09.240 --> 00:32:11.079
were written for me by Sir Witch Doctor.

00:32:11.720 --> 00:32:14.720
I even secretly read
my father and brother's books

00:32:14.880 --> 00:32:15.599
and case files.

00:32:16.359 --> 00:32:18.279
Later I realized they already knew

00:32:18.440 --> 00:32:19.599
but didn't expose me.

00:32:23.480 --> 00:32:23.880
Come here.

00:32:26.580 --> 00:32:27.720
Your Highness, you know what?

00:32:28.160 --> 00:32:29.270
Summers in Qianzhou are hot.

00:32:29.280 --> 00:32:31.820
My father would have my brother
go to the mountains to cut rattan

00:32:31.830 --> 00:32:32.880
and learn to weave mats.

00:32:33.359 --> 00:32:34.839
Every year they made new ones for me.

00:32:35.720 --> 00:32:37.160
It's cooling to lie on this.

00:32:37.240 --> 00:32:38.000
Want to try?

00:32:38.920 --> 00:32:39.319
Sure.

00:32:42.359 --> 00:32:43.319
It really is cool.

00:32:43.519 --> 00:32:44.759
And this mosquito net.

00:32:45.500 --> 00:32:46.880
There were a lot of bugs back home.

00:32:47.279 --> 00:32:47.920
My brother said

00:32:47.960 --> 00:32:49.640
a girl shouldn't get scars from bites,

00:32:49.920 --> 00:32:52.359
so he secretly used his wages
to buy this net for me.

00:32:52.759 --> 00:32:54.039
I'd hang it every summer.

00:32:54.720 --> 00:32:56.160
He thought it would help.

00:32:56.300 --> 00:32:58.200
It's not as good as
my father's mugwort sachet.

00:32:59.599 --> 00:33:00.240
This one.

00:33:02.240 --> 00:33:04.120
Your Highness,
do you want to carry one on you?

00:33:04.440 --> 00:33:07.480
Besides mugwort, my father added
lots of medicinal powders inside.

00:33:07.720 --> 00:33:09.480
We often go into damp places.

00:33:09.559 --> 00:33:10.880
This repels bugs really well.

00:33:13.319 --> 00:33:14.599
Thank you then.

00:33:20.920 --> 00:33:21.519
Chu Chu.

00:33:22.480 --> 00:33:23.359
I'm very happy.

00:33:25.839 --> 00:33:26.720
What?

00:33:27.160 --> 00:33:29.240
I'm happy that you never gave up
being a coroner.

00:33:29.880 --> 00:33:31.839
Because with you,
the only female coroner,

00:33:32.010 --> 00:33:34.120
Three Judicial Offices
could intervene in this case.

00:33:34.200 --> 00:33:35.690
You want to investigate this case too?

00:33:36.640 --> 00:33:38.480
You also think Consort Hui,

00:33:38.519 --> 00:33:41.200
the palace official, and that chief maid
are a bit off?

00:33:41.640 --> 00:33:42.119
Exactly.

00:33:43.319 --> 00:33:44.759
Their reactions to the remains

00:33:45.519 --> 00:33:46.279
were unusual.

00:33:47.279 --> 00:33:49.039
When people are nervous or lying,

00:33:49.160 --> 00:33:50.119
the skin on their face

00:33:50.160 --> 00:33:52.000
involuntarily stiffens and tightens.

00:33:52.480 --> 00:33:55.119
To hide it, they display
inappropriate forced smiles.

00:33:55.120 --> 00:33:56.950
Surrounding skin
will be pulled toward the eyes,

00:33:56.960 --> 00:33:57.640
but the eyes

00:33:57.880 --> 00:33:59.160
don't move at all.

00:33:59.799 --> 00:34:01.759
The eyebrows lift and draw together,

00:34:01.880 --> 00:34:03.839
and their gazes avoid the questioner.

00:34:03.880 --> 00:34:05.359
Blinking increases noticeably.

00:34:05.920 --> 00:34:06.799
Some even

00:34:07.119 --> 00:34:09.400
swallow repeatedly due to a dry throat.

00:34:09.719 --> 00:34:12.360
Forehead, eye sockets,
and sides of the nose start sweating.

00:34:12.679 --> 00:34:15.360
So their reactions
indicate something's wrong.

00:34:16.639 --> 00:34:18.559
They don't want us to take the corpse.

00:34:19.000 --> 00:34:20.119
Or rather, the secret

00:34:20.159 --> 00:34:21.800
behind this corpse involves them.

00:34:21.840 --> 00:34:23.400
No wonder you always say

00:34:23.599 --> 00:34:24.760
a person's expression

00:34:25.480 --> 00:34:26.599
can betray their thoughts.

00:34:27.880 --> 00:34:29.360
When it comes to reading people,

00:34:29.480 --> 00:34:31.920
your husband is one of the best in Tang.

00:34:33.119 --> 00:34:34.000
Really?

00:34:34.880 --> 00:34:36.119
Then in your opinion,

00:34:36.199 --> 00:34:37.559
do I usually look fierce?

00:34:37.840 --> 00:34:39.199
Of course not.

00:34:41.039 --> 00:34:42.199
Stiff face,

00:34:45.679 --> 00:34:46.400
swallowing,

00:34:48.239 --> 00:34:49.280
forced smiles.

00:34:51.039 --> 00:34:52.719
Looks like in your eyes,

00:34:53.159 --> 00:34:55.000
I really am as the capital rumors say,

00:34:55.039 --> 00:34:56.000
not very good-tempered.

00:34:56.440 --> 00:34:56.880
No.

00:34:56.920 --> 00:34:57.320
My dear.

00:34:57.559 --> 00:34:58.800
Hear me out.

00:34:59.400 --> 00:35:01.000
Expressions can be misleading too.

00:35:01.360 --> 00:35:01.880
Also,

00:35:01.920 --> 00:35:02.559
in my opinion,

00:35:03.000 --> 00:35:05.000
a matriarch should be a little imposing.

00:35:05.220 --> 00:35:06.360
It stabilizes the household.

00:35:07.440 --> 00:35:08.440
Imposing?

00:35:17.400 --> 00:35:19.280
You've learned to anticipate things now?

00:35:21.480 --> 00:35:23.400
I'm familiar with the process.

00:35:25.000 --> 00:35:25.599
Alright.

00:35:25.639 --> 00:35:26.199
Here.

00:35:36.079 --> 00:35:38.039
I'll never anticipate again.

00:35:48.480 --> 00:35:49.119
Jinli.

00:35:50.159 --> 00:35:50.690
Your Highness.

00:35:50.719 --> 00:35:51.239
Chu Chu.

00:35:53.100 --> 00:35:54.950
Congratulations,
you finally achieved your wish

00:35:54.960 --> 00:35:56.310
of wearing coroner robes in the palace.

00:35:56.320 --> 00:35:57.220
Thanks to His Highness.

00:35:57.230 --> 00:35:58.360
We couldn't find the corpse.

00:35:58.760 --> 00:35:59.440
I ordered people

00:35:59.480 --> 00:36:00.760
to carefully search

00:36:00.920 --> 00:36:02.170
along where the skull jumped out

00:36:02.380 --> 00:36:03.159
but found nothing.

00:36:04.679 --> 00:36:05.079
Chu Chu.

00:36:06.120 --> 00:36:08.400
You said the deceased
had been dead at least half a year.

00:36:09.920 --> 00:36:11.079
So that would be last winter.

00:36:11.760 --> 00:36:12.719
Last winter was mild.

00:36:12.880 --> 00:36:14.400
When water didn't freeze anywhere,

00:36:14.960 --> 00:36:17.320
the corpse
should have floated in a few days.

00:36:17.740 --> 00:36:19.199
Someone should have found it already.

00:36:19.800 --> 00:36:21.400
Maybe it got stuck between rocks

00:36:21.719 --> 00:36:22.719
when it fell

00:36:23.039 --> 00:36:25.239
or someone tied a weight to it.

00:36:26.719 --> 00:36:27.320
It's possible.

00:36:27.559 --> 00:36:29.360
But we only have the skull,

00:36:29.480 --> 00:36:31.559
so we can't tell how he fell.

00:36:42.760 --> 00:36:44.280
The skull moved with the toad,

00:36:44.760 --> 00:36:47.119
but even if scattered by fish,

00:36:47.280 --> 00:36:48.920
the rest would spread outward

00:36:49.159 --> 00:36:50.159
from the sinking point.

00:36:51.159 --> 00:36:53.210
It should be around
the imperial garden waterways.

00:36:53.320 --> 00:36:53.880
Search again.

00:36:54.030 --> 00:36:55.199
See if there are other clues.

00:37:00.559 --> 00:37:01.800
Lotus Garden has been preparing

00:37:01.810 --> 00:37:03.760
for the Emperor's birthday
these past six months.

00:37:03.960 --> 00:37:05.000
If someone fell in,

00:37:05.400 --> 00:37:06.400
someone would notice.

00:37:07.079 --> 00:37:08.400
It must have happened at night.

00:37:08.559 --> 00:37:09.079
Yes.

00:37:09.239 --> 00:37:10.320
Even with guards at night,

00:37:10.360 --> 00:37:11.679
they patrol according to schedule.

00:37:14.079 --> 00:37:15.800
The shape and position of this rockery

00:37:16.760 --> 00:37:18.239
would cast a large shadow at night.

00:37:18.440 --> 00:37:19.800
Guards might overlook it.

00:37:24.050 --> 00:37:25.490
Enter the water from here and check.

00:37:26.159 --> 00:37:26.440
Yes.

00:37:27.440 --> 00:37:27.920
You all.

00:37:27.930 --> 00:37:28.970
Enter the water from here.

00:37:38.100 --> 00:37:39.119
Your Highness, come here.

00:37:43.239 --> 00:37:45.039
Why are there pumpkin vines here?

00:37:45.400 --> 00:37:46.039
Pumpkin?

00:37:46.519 --> 00:37:46.840
Yes.

00:37:47.639 --> 00:37:50.039
Pumpkins are sown
in early autumn to thrive.

00:37:50.840 --> 00:37:51.519
But

00:37:51.639 --> 00:37:53.119
this spot is shady and dry.

00:37:53.599 --> 00:37:55.639
Seeds dropping in winter
could sprout in spring.

00:37:56.039 --> 00:37:57.719
With suitable temperature and rain,

00:37:57.800 --> 00:37:59.039
they'd still grow.

00:37:59.280 --> 00:38:00.520
It's just that sunlight is poor,

00:38:00.530 --> 00:38:01.690
so it doesn't grow very well.

00:38:02.000 --> 00:38:04.360
This spot looks like
it's been rubbed by something.

00:38:09.800 --> 00:38:10.159
Jinli.

00:38:11.159 --> 00:38:11.559
Here.

00:38:36.741 --> 00:38:39.781
♪Time drips away
like fading crimson scent♪

00:38:39.781 --> 00:38:43.301
♪The hardships of arrival pass
in a fleeting blink♪

00:38:43.661 --> 00:38:46.421
♪Palm lines carry
the footprints of memory♪

00:38:46.901 --> 00:38:50.381
♪Leading us out of every winding turn♪

00:38:51.221 --> 00:38:55.021
♪If two hearts can fly as one
then storms are part of the way♪

00:38:55.021 --> 00:38:58.301
♪Looking back the sky
has already cleared♪

00:38:58.421 --> 00:39:00.941
♪Your branches entwined with mine♪

00:39:00.941 --> 00:39:04.341
♪Bound together in mutual reliance♪

00:39:06.461 --> 00:39:09.541
♪Rugged roads become
the paths of sun and moon♪

00:39:09.541 --> 00:39:12.621
♪Fireflies like stars circle
through the seasons♪

00:39:13.461 --> 00:39:15.581
♪Shining with the hope of dreams♪

00:39:15.581 --> 00:39:20.261
♪This world is no longer in rags♪

00:39:20.981 --> 00:39:24.621
♪Only by holding you in my heart
do I dare embrace fear♪

00:39:24.621 --> 00:39:27.901
♪Quietly waiting for rumors to fade♪

00:39:28.301 --> 00:39:30.621
♪Together we face the tides of fate♪

00:39:30.621 --> 00:39:34.781
♪Turning the course of heaven and earth♪

00:39:34.901 --> 00:39:37.501
♪This love was never easy♪

00:39:37.501 --> 00:39:41.901
♪So life and death will not part us♪

00:39:42.261 --> 00:39:44.821
♪Like sinking into the deep sea♪

00:39:44.821 --> 00:39:49.821
♪The first breath upon awakening♪

00:39:49.821 --> 00:39:52.061
♪This bond will never waver♪

00:39:52.061 --> 00:39:56.941
♪So we stay together
till our hair turns white♪

00:39:56.941 --> 00:39:59.421
♪I ask time itself to hold the pen♪

00:39:59.421 --> 00:40:04.461
♪And write the ending of eternity♪

00:40:04.501 --> 00:40:06.781
♪This love was never easy♪

00:40:06.781 --> 00:40:10.941
♪So I believe without doubt♪

00:40:11.581 --> 00:40:14.181
♪Like a thousand sails passing by♪

00:40:14.181 --> 00:40:19.101
♪Reaching shore
at the first light of dawn♪

00:40:19.581 --> 00:40:21.461
♪This bond will never waver♪

00:40:21.461 --> 00:40:26.461
♪So joy and sorrow
are no longer ours to choose♪

00:40:26.461 --> 00:40:28.861
♪I will prove it
with the rest of my life♪

00:40:28.861 --> 00:40:34.621
♪Together at the edge
of the world without an end♪